What you are using
--------------------------------------------------------------------
VSBS is a zero-touch, safety-first, fully cited agentic system for
autonomous vehicle service booking. Every architectural choice inside
it is grounded in peer-reviewed research, international standards
(ISO 13374, ISO 21448 SOTIF, ISO 26262, ISO 3779, WCAG 2.2 AAA,
FIPS 203 / 204 / 205, DPDP 2025), and production vendor documentation.
See docs/research/ for the full citation trail — eight cited research
reports plus an architecture synthesis, a PhD-grade foundation you
inherit the moment you pick this up.

