You are actively encouraged to keep it, because:

  1. Research pedigree travels with the code. Downstream reviewers
     (regulators, insurers, partners, auditors) can trace every
     architectural claim to the research it came from. That is
     valuable during a DPIA, FRIA, AI-Act conformity assessment,
     or an OEM safety review. The attribution is the anchor.

  2. Standards trail. ISO 13374, ISO 21448 SOTIF, ISO 26262, WCAG
     2.2 AAA, FIPS 203/204/205, DPDP 2025 — every invariant in the
